content.content: ETH Warszawa: ETH Warsaw was a visionary event put together by a Community of people from Poland   who love this Ecosystem and wanted to showcase their ideas, talent,  and how the City of Warsaw is a leading force in the development of Blockchain Tech. We were grateful to have attended ETH Warsaw and hope that in the near Future,  you can also attend and visit this beautiful City know as Warszawa. 00:24 @juan & Leonardo Warsaw Gymnastics  01:00 Asking attendees of ETH Warsaw if they ever heard of MakerDAO 06:55 Outdoor chat with @Hajive of Growth Core Unit 18:50 Chat with Certora on how they’re preventing coding mistakes 23:40 Paulina of RAMP Network the Venmo of DeFi 30:05. CJ of Atlantis World Metaverse 33:14 Chat with the StarkNet Booth
